Description
-----------

This Cvar defines how many different sounds are played for each [sound
shader](Sound_%28decl%29 "Sound (decl)") .

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    s_maxSoundsPerShader [Int]

Parameters
----------

-   [Int] - Sets the number of sounds.

